Autocompleted.description: Indicates that the order was auto completed with force by a user.

CustomTaxesApplied.description: CustomTaxesApplied indicates that the order has custom taxes applied and other processes should not touch the taxes anymore.

HasReturnLines.description: Indicates the order contains lines that have negative quantities to ship, aka, are returned lines.

ImportedFromLiveGuard.description: Indicates that this order was created in localmode on liveguard and pushed to the cloud.

IsReturned.description: Indicates that this order has been returned, partially or completely, by another order.

IsReturnReversal.description: Indicates that the order is the result of a return reversal.

Repairs.description: Indicates that the order is a repair order and contains products used during a repair

Replenishment.description: Replenishment indicates that this order is used to replenish a store/warehouse

Restitution.description: Indicates that the order is a restitution order

ReturnToSupplier.description: ReturnToSupplier indicates that the order will be returned from the store back to the supplier (RMA/CMA).

SoldByOverridden.description: Indicates that the SoldBy, which is normally determined automatically, has been manually overriden on the Order level.
